IPC
===

3 types of services:

Port: communication end-point
IPC address (32b): 16b seat ID + 16b port ID

Seat: processor
Seat manager

Port name: "seat:function"

Zone: collection of IPC seats communicating to each other
Zone manager (a.k.a IPC Master)


